      "id": "redundant-controls-rule",
      "content": "UI Generation Rule: If the UI includes separate 'Turn On' and 'Turn Off' buttons for a device, you MUST NOT also include a 'Toggle' button for that same device. The 'On' and 'Off' buttons make a 'Toggle' button redundant and confusing.",
